title: Shifted Maze
author: jimmythelynx
description:
Shifted Maze 1.0
A new take on the classical 2D maze. There's only one unique maze that is randomly shifted. The defuser must navigate to three coordinates in order.
Little edgework required.

Module ID: shiftedMaze

Created by: jimmythelynx

A huge shout out to Royal_Flu$h whose video tutorial kickstarted my modding ambitions.
The module is using a sound file taken from "Symbolic Coordinates" by Royal_Flu$h.
